{"word":"G1687 - ἐμβατεύω - embateúō - em-bat-yoo'-o - Intrude into","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐμβατεύω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">embateúō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">em-bat-yoo'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Intrude into</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - நுழை"},{"paragraph":"to enter"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1722 - ἐν - en - en/1722\">G1722</a> and a presumed derivative of the base of <a href=\"#/G939 - βάσις - básis - bas'-ece/939\">G939</a>; equivalent to <a href=\"#/G1684 - ἐμβαίνω - embaínō - em-ba'-hee-no/1684\">G1684</a>; to <i>intrude on</i> (figuratively): - intrude into.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}